%% Diagram: Vitess migration timeline (2016–2020)
%% Type: timeline
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
timeline
    title Slack's Vitess migration (2016–2020)
    2016 : Evaluation begins
         : Enterprise Grid drives requirement
    2017 : First production workload (RSS feed)
         : Routing layer + diff-read tooling
    2018 : Table-by-table migration starts
         : Disasterpiece Theater chaos program begins
    2019 : Strategy shifts to whole-shard migration
         : Flannel rolled out
         : HAProxy → Envoy migration starts
    2020 : 99% MySQL traffic on Vitess
         : COVID surge handled via online resharding
         : Multi-region deployment for data residency
